Amtrak, New Jersey Transit Halt Service to Check Gas Leak Near Elizabeth

-- B y   P e t e r   J .   B r e n n a n
-- 
2011-05-31T16:51:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/amtrak-new-jersey-transit-halt-service-to-check-gas-leak-near-elizabeth.html
Amtrak  and  New Jersey Transit  said
they suspended Northeast Corridor service as police and fire
departments investigate a reported gas leak in Elizabeth,  New
Jersey .  Amtrak said it suspended its service between  New York City 
and Philadelphia while New Jersey Transit said its Northeast
Corridor and North Jersey Coast routes have been halted. The
information was disclosed in two separate e-mailed statements.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter J. Brennan at 
 pbrennan3@bloomberg.net  